				<td colspan="2"><span>I agree - fairly useless song.  I haven't used it since about lvl 20.  It is in Katta on the moon.  A hard zone to get too unless you have help.  If you get a Translocate from a wizard to Twighlight Sea (sp?) then you are probably safe with invis.  I would recommend waiting till higher level when you need the other more useful songs from Katta like Amplification.  Then you can pick up the song just to have it.  
