				<td colspan="2"><span>You should definitely check out the Guides section here (link on the left).  In the guide I wrote on AFK Training, you will find what is perhaps one of the only real uses for the Food Song, afk training String and/or Singing skill without eating food, hehe.  Oh, if you are on a corpse run, it also stops the annoying &quot;You are out of food&quot; spams.
<br />

<br />
A run to Katta Kastellum is most certainly in order by level 30, because Amplification is most certainly worth having.
<br />

<br />
Also, if you do not yet have a Combine Lute or Combine Mandolin, you should run to Katta and buy one from the vendors there.  Its 2.2 mod is the best you will likely find until your midlevels or higher.  (Check out the guide on how instruments work to learn about modifiers etc. and check the Instruments link for a list of instruments and their modifiers)</span></td>
